data.description: Welcome to this charming 1116 square foot home that's ready to delight its new owners! With recent exterior paint, this residence boasts fresh curb appeal and is nestled in the highly sought-after Northside School District. Location couldn't be better! You're just minutes away from major routes like 1604 and 151, providing easy access to all parts of the city. Plus, you're close to the excitement of SeaWorld and convenient shopping options. Here, you'll find the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and entertainment.    Key Features: 1116 Square Feet, 3 Bedrooms and 1 Bathroom: Enjoy a cozy yet spacious living environment that offers both comfort and functionality.    Fresh Exterior Paint: The home has been thoughtfully updated with recent exterior paint, enhancing its appearance and durability.    Newer Roof: The roof is only 5.5 years old, providing peace of mind and potential savings on maintenance costs.    Northside School District: Families will appreciate the excellent educational opportunities provided by the renowned Northside School District, ensuring a top-tier education for your loved ones.    Easy Highway Access: Commuting is a breeze with convenient highway access nearby, making it effortless to reach your destination whether for work or leisure.    Shopping Centers: This home's location is a shopper's paradise, with numerous shopping centers in close proximity. Explore a variety of stores and boutiques, and take advantage of the convenience of nearby grocery shopping.    Restaurants and Entertainment: Satisfy your culinary cravings with an array of restaurants just around the corner. Additionally, enjoy easy access to entertainment options, making it simple to enjoy your downtime with family and friends.    This charming home offers a wonderful blend of comfort and convenience in a highly desirable location. Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours and experience the best of Northside living. Schedule a viewing today and see all that this property has to offer!
